Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:10.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:40.35,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The strong will survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:42.79,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,and the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:47.02,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:53.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.16,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.41,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he has that recovery magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:10.23,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:11.61,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Stupidsta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:19.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first peasant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:23.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,that I, a royal, ever acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:29.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,defeat that guy, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:38.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw enough at him from the both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.49,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,...that weakling, disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'll let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:48.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:30.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:35.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:39.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:44.14,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:47.45,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:50.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.06,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:58.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.11,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:11.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:17.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:24.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:28.05,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:31.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.53,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction and Salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:51.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, I'm fine now, so please \Njust take care of Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:59.09,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.22,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if my remaining \Nmagic will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.70,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.38,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Where's all that energy you just had?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.08,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die before I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.86,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.19,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, is the training painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:34.75,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,When things get rough,\Nremember the faces of those you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:40.25,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,We were born to protect the people \Nof this kingdom that we love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:59.77,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Once we become strong enough to protect\Nthis kingdom, we'll be allowed to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:03.04,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,You'll probably make it out first, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.03,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:09.55,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're the strongest \Nout of all of us, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.04,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.28,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.90,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Until you get out, too, Fana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.21,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Let's go see the \Noutside world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.47,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,This is your final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.70,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,Kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:42.44,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,The sole survivor will be allowed to go \Noutside as our kingdom's mage warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.14,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse, you'll all be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.90,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.42,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.81,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.56,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.04,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Mars is the one who survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.06,flashback,Trainer 2,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's implant him with the magic stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:06.25,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go ahead and give him\NFana's powers, too, since she was
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.19,flashback,Trainer,0000,0000,0000,,the last one he killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:12.29,flashback,Trainer 2,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll finally have the \Nultimate mage warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:21.38,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... fine alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:25.38,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,because I have extremely powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.54,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Those without magic are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:31.47,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And the weak will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.22,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:36.81,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,...still moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.31,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It can't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:45.81,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as na√Øve as you \Ncannot win against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.67,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:01.96,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,His flame recovery magic should've \Nbeen negated by Asta's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.67,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect opportunity \Nto finish him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:09.05,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more... Just a little more, \Nand I can break through these restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.17,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.54,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:23.04,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what spell I pick from\Nmy grimoire, I won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:27.61,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.57,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yuno just do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.99,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:52.40,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The spell... has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.83,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:57.72,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Was that magic? What did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.85,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.05,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There was a little girl, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.61,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.82,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.46,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:12.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.38,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,we've defeated him for sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.85,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.81,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,the characters from that scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.57,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.49,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.25,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The dungeon is falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Wind Ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.75,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.28,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa, take care of Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.30,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.86,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:42.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Save him... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.01,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.89,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:55.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,came to conquer this dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:12:00.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not... to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:15.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It might be a waste to let \Nsomeone that strong die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late! We won't make \Nit out in time. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.45,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:37.94,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa can't use her \NMagic Flower Guidepost right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.53,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Go right. I'll guide us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.66,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.62,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.27,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.07,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.74,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,More coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.69,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:39.63,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've already acknowledged \Nyou as my... as our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.29,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.51,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,...Asta die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.80,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,...alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:29.59,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.55,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.75,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:33.81,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:42.82,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Man... We sure were lucky \Nthey created a path for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:49.57,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this old man's ultimate \Ntrump card, Hermit's Thick Smoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.83,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,they never realized we were \Nclose by the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:15:00.54,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thank goodness you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.59,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.53,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.43,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:13.55,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.50,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.29,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.93,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:04.27,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't do that, you wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.15,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.46,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:26.17,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you awake, Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.43,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.79,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Great work back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:35.18,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I was able \Nto get all this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.72,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Now the people of our kingdom, \Nas well as my daughters,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.70,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,will be able to eat delicious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:01.45,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:05.55,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you go see the world outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:09.97,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,For me... as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.72,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.98,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.48,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.78,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You can actually say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:47.92,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.25,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.96,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:58.70,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! As long as you're okay, Stupidsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:02.55,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievable.\NYour recuperative ability is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.51,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's resilient, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, Yuno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:14.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more than just resilient... ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:19.24,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry! I didn't have \Nenough magic to fully heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:23.47,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I just did what I could for now, \Nso you probably shouldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,N-No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:29.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.53,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,N-No problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.63,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:39.58,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to \Ndie before I got to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:42.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die. Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not until I become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.25,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going \Nto be the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup. Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use my body as a crutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? \NIt's not like I'm hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.37,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:14.93,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.59,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:29.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so ashamed that I didn't acknowledge \Nyou just because you were peasants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,magnificent Magic Knights \Nof the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.16,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:50.73,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:53.43,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffocating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Four-Eyes... it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What?! And after I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you were such a good four-eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.25,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too serious, Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.69,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.69,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:24.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noelle. Your clothes are all ripped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.03,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.04,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help myself! Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:40.42,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.26,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.68,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:35.70,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:38.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:45.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:51.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:53.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:56.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:05.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:10.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:15.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.45,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:21.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:27.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:31.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
