Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:45.47,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:49.84,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}So You Can Actually\NSay Things Like That
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:49.26,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,So You Can Actually Say Things Like That.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:54.10,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.87,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:02.26,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You can actually say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:05.11,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:09.11,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:11.34,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,She sells seashells by the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:13.21,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:15.78,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,How much wood could a woodchuck chuck \Nif a woodchuck could chuck wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:17.12,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:19.61,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,She sells... she shells... seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:22.35,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Piper picked... \Na pick of peckled pippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:24.38,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,How much wood could... \Na woodchuck... chuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:26.63,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:28.38,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.75,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,She sells she shells by the she shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:32.95,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Piper pipped a \Npep of pippled peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:35.82,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,How much wood could a \Nwoodchuck... could... chuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.82,0:23:37.02,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! Did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:47.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?! We just met the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:50.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 20:\N"Assembly at the Royal Capital."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:55.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 20\N\N{\fs18} Assembly at the Royal Capital
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Being loud is my magic!
